Weatherford International

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search


Weatherford





Type

Public


Traded as
NYSE: WFT


Industry
Oilfield services & equipment


Founded
1940s


Headquarters
Switzerland (incorporation)



Key people

Chairman: William E. Macaulay CEO: Mark A. McCollum


